lder openspec\"\n27f375b8 — 2026-03-30 09:08 — \"chore: implement prettier\"\n```\n\n**Các bug fix hôm nay chưa được push lên git** — workspace DTLX BE hiện tại **không có git**. Code chạy local trong `dist/` nhưng không có repo git để push lên GitLab.\n\n### Hướng xử lý\n\nMuốn đẩy các bug fix (4 bugs đã fix) lên GitLab để trigger pipeline không?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":123,"output":549,"totalTokens":147883,"cacheRead":145105,"cacheWrite":2106,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776162143517,"responseId":"062d486107384787d72be69212a976dc","__openclaw":{"id":"02d899f5","seq":1257}},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | 11:15 UTC 14 Apr\n\nActive sessions: 4\n• cron:6f3323ef (5p Progress - DTLX): running — Heartbeat monitor, webchat — ~23h 20m\n• cron:ed2d0b5d (5p Progress Report): running — Heartbeat monitor, webchat — ~23h 2m\n• heartbeat (main): done — Last run ~11:15 UTC, silent exit ✅\n• cron:e7885813 (Agent Status): running — This check, Telegram → Lead ✅\n\nPipeline: **HEALTHY** ✅\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\n• Blockers: None\n• Telegram: OK ✅\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}],"timestamp":1776165430245,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e","sourceTool":"sessions_send"},"__openclaw":{"id":"0c1fcc53","seq":1258}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is an inter-session heartbeat message from cron:e7885813. No user prompt here - this is just a system status report. I should reply HEARTBEAT_OK since the pipeline is healthy and there are no issues that need attention."},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":58,"totalTokens":143540,"cacheRead":6727,"cacheWrite":136755,"cost":{"total":0}},"